org.knime.base.node.mine.bayes.naivebayes.datamodel2

Class PMMLNaiveBayesModelTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.base.node.mine.bayes.naivebayes.datamodel2.PMMLNaiveBayesModelTranslator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PMMLTranslator

    public class PMMLNaiveBayesModelTranslator
extends Object
implements PMMLTranslator
    Helper class translate between the internal used naive Bayes model and the PMML standard. The class also provides helper methods to read/write extensions.
    Author:
    Tobias Koetter
